data.description: Fantastic 2 story townhome with spacious Open floor plan featuring 2 Primary bedrooms with en-suite baths! Gorgeous living area with vaulted ceiling and sliding doors out to the courtyard. Formal dining and kitchen open to the living area. It's The Perfect home for Entertaining! Kitchen with beautiful counters, tiled backsplash, stainless steel appliances, electric cooktop, and walk in pantry. Home has tons of natural light, stunning wood look laminate floors throughout, tiled wet areas, and extra storage under the stairs. Powder room for guests on the main floor. Two car attached garage with opener.  Community garden area and daily courtesy patrol for the neighborhood. A Great Location within minutes to a choice of restaurants and shopping, and Hackberry Park with walking trails and playground. Easy access to Hwy 6, I-10, and Beltway 8. Low Tax Rate! Hurry, Call Today Before It's gone!
